extendedInfo.description: SES - The Leading Search & Social Marketing Event - brings its world renowned learning experience and thought leaders in the digital marketing field to Singapore once again. More than 50 speakers from a cross-section of well-respected industry organisations will discuss the latest market dynamics and trends, best practices, technology and innovation.SES Singapore 2011 will be packed with sessions and labs focused on education (no sales pitches!), covering search marketing, social media, keyword research, local advertising, mobile engagement, link building, multiple site issues, online video, site optimization and usability, in addition to high-level strategy, keynotes, networking events, parties and more.
